channel.title: [317] PwnZ0rtZScape [317]
channel.description:
My server is, like u see in the title, a 317 server. The credits goes to: Me, for the coding and editing etc. Server Owner Brian, for the source Homiescape.
Im not a prof in java, but i keep getting better in moparscape (with moparscape i mean RSPS). Like, the first time i heard of it, i thought it was a big game looking like RS and what u need to pay for to play. Now, im coding in a server and i know what it is etc.
This server isn't like the others, like that when u hit 1, ur level will be 126 and the skill 99. On this server, u don't get too fast xp, but too not too slow. So in the middle.
Now, this server isn't really little.
Features: Herblore works, but not fully. Still going to update. Fletching, bows and arrows, arrows made by me, bows by (i think) brian. Cooking, but sadly not fully, what works: U can cook all fishes, expect sharks (if i got time, i think i will fix it). And pie works, but not all, still going to update that too. Ranged works. Thieving works, but im going to change things. Woodcutting doesn't really work. Like u get 100k when u cut an oak tree. If i find out how to, i will make it normal.
Here are some pics with a descripition:
[IMG]http://img534.imageshack.us/img534/6231/screenshot0006.png[/img]
Like you can see, fletching works.
U can make bows and arrows (BTW that place was old home that Brian made). I don't got much to tell about this.
[IMG]http://img46.imageshack.us/img46/3233/screenshot0005.png[/img]
That is the training place made by ME. There are Jogre's, Barbarian Womans and Mans As far as i know, that place has never been used before.
[IMG]http://img94.imageshack.us/img94/2761/screenshot0003.png[/img]
That is the home i made. It's in Lumbrdige, i think you can see it if u look at the caste :P.
[IMG]http://img215.imageshack.us/img215/6300/screenshot0001.png[/img]
TzHaar cave, it isn't good. Im still going to update it.
[IMG]http://img535.imageshack.us/img535/2266/screenshot0000.png[/img]
The shop place. Isn't made by me like i say in the text. Only the items IN the shops are edited by me.....
Well, this topic isn't real big. Im still going to update it.
BTW: No download link.....
